  m_Name: Anne Phayquname
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterSystem:
    characterName: Anne Phayquname
    hejFras: Oh, are you talking to me?
    hejFrasEvent:
      Guid:
        Data1: 770839133
        Data2: 1248789310
        Data3: 1274628287
        Data4: -1630003170
      Path: event:/Ann/Ann Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: "Shouldn\u2019t a cookie like yourself be out dancing? "
      answer: 'Oh I wish. I can really cook with helium on the dancefloor! In the
        Bronx they call me the Jive Queen! If I could I would be out all night! '
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: "Holy mackerel! What\u2019s the best music to dance to? "
      answer: "Well when they start shreddin\u2019 on that licorice stick, ooooh
        baby that\u2019s that good stuff! That's when I really cut a rug! I wouldn\u2019t
        mind taking a piece of cake like you to a dance sometime\u2026 "
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "Jeepers! You're pretty forward aren\u2019t you! "
      answer: "Well, I know what I like, and I\u2019m not afraid of a little light
        hearted flirting! Maybe I should be a bit more careful with who I lead on,
        there aren\u2019t many out there that can handle my\u2026 \u201Cspecial\u201D
        lifestyle\u2026 "
    secondQuestion:
      question: "I\u2019m guessing they only serve the best booze in town here! "
      answer: "HA! Gods no! I saw a bottle in the back that cost less than the glass
        it\u2019s served in! I would never be seen drinking that cheesy crap. "
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'You seem to have an expensive taste! '
      answer: 'Excuse you, I have GREAT taste! Not my fault you have to spend some
        greenbacks for the good stuff. '
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "Maybe you could show me the \u201Cgood stuff\u201D sometime? "
      answer: "Asking out the staff at a ball? My my! As long as it\u2019s not in
        the morning, I can never seem to wake up on time\u2026 "
    thirdQuestion:
      question: 'Have you been dusting the same shelf for 30 minutes? '
      answer: "Eeeeeh yes! Allford always wants it to be squeaky clean! Have you
        been watching me? Hope that cop over there isn\u2019t as vigilant as you\u2026 "
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Do you have something to hide? I can keep a secret. '
      answer: "Ok, but promise to not tell anyone, you feel like someone I can trust.
        I\u2019m not actually a maid, I\u2019m a burglar who has stolen a lot of
        cash! I almost got out with the lettuce, but then I saw my ex in the corner!
        That dandy would definitely recognise me, so I stole this maid outfit and
        here I am! "
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "What a story! How\u2019d you get in? "
      answer: "Through a window ofcourse! Thankfully I\u2019m not scared of heights!
        But I\u2019m not off the hook yet. Say, you wouldn\u2019t mind switching
        duds? I think you\u2019d look swell in a maid outfit! "
    "hejD\xE5Fras": "Back to my\u2026 \u201Cduties\u201D."
